SUMMARY:The Write Stuff! Creative Writing Group
DESCRIPTION:If you enjoy creative writing or would like to try it for the first time\, then this Creative Writing Workshop may be just the place for you. Everyone will work together to explore creative writing in a safe\, open\, and encouraging environment. You may bring a short story or chapter from a larger body of work for peer feedback. 18+ only.
URL:https://unitedarts.org/calendar/the-write-stuff-creative-writing-group/2026-03-19/
LOCATION:Southeast Regional Library\, 908 7th Avenue\, Garner\, 27529
CATEGORIES:Workshop
